{"question": "Kako se vpišem v višji letnik?", "language": "sl", "answer": "V pisemnom dokumentu je opisano, kako se vpišejo v višji letnik na študijskem programu. Najboljši korak je, da se prijavite z digitalno identiteto UL-ID v sistem STUDIS. Potrebno je klikniti na povezavo » Izpolnjujete pogoje za vpis« in vnesite ali spremnite svoje osebnih podatke na vpisnem listu. Nakonek se lahko izbira predmeti in izpolnjuje pogoji za napredovanje v višji letnik.", "keyword_hit_rate": 1.0, "retrieval_hit": null, "recall_at_k": null, "mrr_at_k": null, "ndcg_at_k": null, "first_relevant_rank": null, "retrieved_doc_ids": ["9e13d0e5e65b", "5225780dda0b", "a3e1647a6ba3", "a3e1647a6ba3"], "chunk_hit": null, "chunk_recall_at_k": null, "chunk_precision_at_k": null, "chunk_mrr_at_k": null, "chunk_ndcg_at_k": null, "chunk_first_relevant_rank": null, "retrieved_chunk_ids": ["9e13d0e5e65b_chunk0000", "5225780dda0b_chunk0001", "a3e1647a6ba3_chunk0002", "a3e1647a6ba3_chunk0000"], "retrieved_keyword_hit": true, "retrieved_keyword_first_rank": 1, "retrieval_weak": false, "is_negative": false, "negative_ok": null, "scores": [7.379393577575684, 4.685331344604492, 3.345878839492798, 2.8625662326812744], "retrieved": [{"doc_id": "9e13d0e5e65b", "chunk_id": "9e13d0e5e65b_chunk0000", "title": "Vpis v višji letnik", "section": "main", "url": "https://www.fri.uni-lj.si/sl/vpis-v-visji-letnik", "score": 7.379393577575684, "pre_rerank_score": 0.6599428653717041, "rerank_score": 7.379393577575684, "vector_score": 0.8651179671287537, "bm25_score": 12.211159101268152}, {"doc_id": "5225780dda0b", "chunk_id": "5225780dda0b_chunk0001", "title": "Vpis v višji letnik", "section": "main", "url": "https://fri.uni-lj.si/sl/vpis-v-visji-letnik", "score": 4.685331344604492, "pre_rerank_score": 0.596718430519104, "rerank_score": 4.685331344604492, "vector_score": 0.8532333374023438, "bm25_score": 9.67425375777956}, {"doc_id": "a3e1647a6ba3", "chunk_id": "a3e1647a6ba3_chunk0002", "title": "Pogosta vprašanja", "se